---
title: Blackened Catfish with Crispy Potatoes and Blistered Summer Vegetables
description: Typically battered and fried, catfish is a staple of Southern cooking. For a lighter preparation, we’re blackening this flaky fish with a potent mix of spices. A side of crispy roasted potatoes and caramelized vegetables compliments the dish; a sprinkling of chopped cilantro and a wedge of lemon brightens it up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55c279aff8b25e97088b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/55c279aff8b25e97088b4567.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/blackened-catfish-55c279aff8b25e97088b4567
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: North America
